{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778974735805,"sessionID":"ses_1ccd7dd61ffepBfm6K05Htdrlc","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_boLfmody9q5m0P4yj26dddk9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":2000},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"id: GO:0102177\\nname: 24-methylenelophenol methyl oxidase activity\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: 24-methylenelophenol + O2 + NADH + H+ = 4alpha-hydroxymethyl-ergosta-7,24(241)-dien-3beta-ol + NAD + H2O.\\\" [GOC:pz, PMID:11707264, RHEA:58872]\\nxref: EC:1.14.18.11 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}\\nxref: MetaCyc:RXN-11930\\nxref: RHEA:58872 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}\\nis_a: GO:0016709 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on paired donors, with incorporation or reduction of molecular oxygen, NAD(P)H as one donor, and incorporation of one atom of oxygen\\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \\\"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30193\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n\\n\\nEC:1.14.18.11 (xref above) does not match the rest of the GO term description:\\nName: plant 4alpha-monomethylsterol monooxygenase\\nreaction: 24-methylidenelophenol + 6 Fe(II)-[cytochrome b5] + 3 O2 + 5 H(+) = 4alpha-carboxy-ergosta-7,24(24(1))-dien-3beta-ol + 6 Fe(III)-[cytochrome b5] + 4 H2O\\nhas RHEA xref: RHEA:58868\\n\\nRHEA:58872 (xref above) is \\\"part of RHEA:58868\\\", and has this reaction:\\n24-methylidenelophenol + 2 Fe(II)-[cytochrome b5] + O2 + 2 H(+) = 4alpha-hydroxymethyl-ergosta-7,24(24(1))-dien-3beta-ol + 2 Fe(III)-[cytochrome b5] + H2O.\\n\\n\\nThere are 3 IEA (via EC:1.14.18.11) annotations to GO:0102177 by UniProt to Arabidopsis Methylsterol monooxygenase SMO1-3, SMO2-1 and SMO2-2.\\n\\nTasks:\\n- [x] Change RHEA def and term xref to RHEA:58868 (and remove the unnecessary GOC:pz def xref)\\n- [x] Change MetaCyc xref to MetaCyc:RXN-19724\\n- [x] Update name to '4alpha-monomethylsterol monooxygenase activity' to match EC\\n- [x] Update def to \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: 24-methylidenelophenol + 6 Fe(II)-[cytochrome b5] + 3 O2 + 5 H+ = 4alpha-carboxy-ergosta-7,24(24(1))-dien-3beta-ol + 6 Fe(III)-[cytochrome b5] + 4 H2O\\\"\\n- [x] Change parent to GO:0016716 (EC:1.14.18.- )\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [],\n4:   \"title\": \"GO:0102177 24-methylenelophenol methyl oxidase activity\",\n5:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31985\"\n6: }\n\n(End of file - total 6 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"id: GO:0102177\\nname: 24-methylenelophenol methyl oxidase activity\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: 24-methylenelophenol + O2 + NADH + H+ = 4alpha-hydroxymethyl-ergosta-7,24(241)-dien-3beta-ol + NAD + H2O.\\\" [GOC:pz, PMID:11707264, RHEA:58872]\\nxref: EC:1.14.18.11 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}\\nxref: MetaCyc:RXN-11930\\nxref: RHEA:58872 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}\\nis_a: GO:0016709 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on paired donors, with incorporation or reduction of molecular oxygen, NAD(P)H as one donor, and incorporation of one atom of oxygen\\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \\\"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30193\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n\\n\\nEC:1.14.18.11 (xref above) does not match the rest of the GO term description:\\nName: plant 4alpha-monomethylsterol monooxygenase\\nreaction: 24-methylidenelophenol + 6 Fe(II)-[cytochrome b5] + 3 O2 + 5 H(+) = 4alpha-carboxy-ergosta-7,24(24(1))-dien-3beta-ol + 6 Fe(III)-[cytochrome b5] + 4 H2O\\nhas RHEA xref: RHEA:58868\\n\\nRHEA:58872 (xref above) is \\\"part of RHEA:58868\\\", and has this reaction:\\n24-methylidenelophenol + 2 Fe(II)-[cytochrome b5] + O2 + 2 H(+) = 4alpha-hydroxymethyl-ergosta-7,24(24(1))-dien-3beta-ol + 2 Fe(III)-[cytochrome b5] + H2O.\\n\\n\\nThere are 3 IEA (via EC:1.14.18.11) annotations to GO:0102177 by UniProt to Arabidopsis Methylsterol monooxygenase SMO1-3, SMO2-1 and SMO2-2.\\n\\nTasks:\\n- [x] Change RHEA def and term xref to RHEA:58868 (and remove the unnecessary GOC:pz def xref)\\n- [x] Change MetaCyc xref to MetaCyc:RXN-19724\\n- [x] Update name to '4alpha-monomethylsterol monooxygenase activity' to match EC\\n- [x] Update def to \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: 24-methylidenelophenol + 6 Fe(II)-[cytochrome b5] + 3 O2 + 5 H+ = 4alpha-carboxy-ergosta-7,24(24(1))-dien-3beta-ol + 6 Fe(III)-[cytochrome b5] + 4 H2O\\\"\\n- [x] Change parent to GO:0016716 (EC:1.14.18.- )\\n\",\n  \"comments\": [],\n  \"title\": \"GO:0102177 24-methylenelophenol methyl oxidase activity\",\n  \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31985\"\n}","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778974735748,"end":1778974735802}},"id":"prt_e33283d710011IpiF6gzAmhBqC","sessionID":"ses_1ccd7dd61ffepBfm6K05Htdrlc","messageID":"msg_e332823b3001RM8K4832ZUH6AK"}}
