{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778975248239,"sessionID":"ses_1ccd7dd61ffepBfm6K05Htdrlc","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_ueI64aDc6b9WYCE3JuiSZi3N","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/references_cache/PMID_11707264.md","offset":1,"limit":200},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/references_cache/PMID_11707264.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: reference_id: PMID:11707264\n3: title: Functional identification of sterol-4alpha-methyl oxidase cDNAs from Arabidopsis thaliana by complementation of a yeast erg25 mutant lacking sterol-4alpha-methyl oxidation.\n4: authors:\n5: - Darnet S\n6: - Bard M\n7: - Rahier A\n8: journal: FEBS Lett\n9: year: '2001'\n10: doi: 10.1016/s0014-5793(01)03002-2\n11: keywords:\n12: - \"Arabidopsis/enzymology, genetics\"\n13: - \"Arabidopsis Proteins/chemistry, classification, genetics, metabolism\"\n14: - \"Chromatography, Gas\"\n15: - \"Cloning, Molecular\"\n16: - \"DNA, Complementary\"\n17: - Ergosterol/biosynthesis\n18: - \"Isoenzymes/chemistry, genetics, metabolism\"\n19: - \"Mixed Function Oxygenases/chemistry, classification, genetics, metabolism\"\n20: - Molecular Sequence Data\n21: - Molecular Structure\n22: - Mutation\n23: - Oxidation-Reduction\n24: - Phylogeny\n25: - \"Phytosterols/chemistry, metabolism\"\n26: - \"Saccharomyces cerevisiae/enzymology, genetics\"\n27: content_type: abstract_only\n28: ---\n29: \n30: # Functional identification of sterol-4alpha-methyl oxidase cDNAs from Arabidopsis thaliana by complementation of a yeast erg25 mutant lacking sterol-4alpha-methyl oxidation.\n31: **Authors:** Darnet S, Bard M, Rahier A\n32: **Journal:** FEBS Lett (2001)\n33: **DOI:** [10.1016/s0014-5793(01)03002-2](https://doi.org/10.1016/s0014-5793(01)03002-2)\n34: \n35: ## Content\n36: \n37: 1. FEBS Lett. 2001 Nov 9;508(1):39-43. doi: 10.1016/s0014-5793(01)03002-2.\n38: \n39: Functional identification of sterol-4alpha-methyl oxidase cDNAs from Arabidopsis \n40: thaliana by complementation of a yeast erg25 mutant lacking sterol-4alpha-methyl \n41: oxidation.\n42: \n43: Darnet S(1), Bard M, Rahier A.\n44: \n45: Author information:\n46: (1)Département Isoprénoïdes, Institut de Biologie Moléculaire des Plantes, \n47: UPR-CNRS 2357, 28 rue Goethe, 67083 Strasbourg Cedex, France.\n48: \n49: Specific primers derived from both genomic sequence data and EST cDNA sequences \n50: were used to polymerase chain reaction amplify two full-length cDNA sequences \n51: (AtSMO1 and AtSMO2), 801 and 783 bp, respectively, from an Arabidopsis thaliana \n52: cDNA library. The predicted proteins show 32 and 29% identity to the ERG25 gene \n53: from Saccharomyces cerevisiae which encodes the sterol-4alpha-methyl oxidase \n54: (SMO), a membrane-bound non-heme di-iron oxygenase involved in lipid metabolism. \n55: Heterologous expression of AtSMO1 and AtSMO2 in a yeast erg25 ergosterol \n56: auxotroph, lacking SMO activity, restored growth and endogenous ergosterol \n57: synthesis. These results represent the first functional identification of SMO \n58: genes from plants.\n59: \n60: DOI: 10.1016/s0014-5793(01)03002-2\n61: PMID: 11707264 [Indexed for MEDLINE]\n\n(End of file - total 61 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\nreference_id: PMID:11707264\ntitle: Functional identification of sterol-4alpha-methyl oxidase cDNAs from Arabidopsis thaliana by complementation of a yeast erg25 mutant lacking sterol-4alpha-methyl oxidation.\nauthors:\n- Darnet S\n- Bard M\n- Rahier A\njournal: FEBS Lett\nyear: '2001'\ndoi: 10.1016/s0014-5793(01)03002-2\nkeywords:\n- \"Arabidopsis/enzymology, genetics\"\n- \"Arabidopsis Proteins/chemistry, classification, genetics, metabolism\"\n- \"Chromatography, Gas\"\n- \"Cloning, Molecular\"\n- \"DNA, Complementary\"\n- Ergosterol/biosynthesis\n- \"Isoenzymes/chemistry, genetics, metabolism\"\n- \"Mixed Function Oxygenases/chemistry, classification, genetics, metabolism\"\n- Molecular Sequence Data","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"references_cache/PMID_11707264.md","time":{"start":1778975248222,"end":1778975248237}},"id":"prt_e33300c99001AVnCNNdM2oDGON","sessionID":"ses_1ccd7dd61ffepBfm6K05Htdrlc","messageID":"msg_e333007010011wKNmbHOkzLCyl"}}
